      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of label and caption for satellite image on Dec 3 with article on prospects for government action on climate change regarding one area cited</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A label and a caption for a satellite image in Science Times on Tuesday with an article about the prospects for government action on climate change referred incorrectly to an area off the Bahamas where coral reefs are threatened by global warming. Most of the area, the Great Bahama Bank, is sand under shallow water. It is not entirely coral reef.</p>
      </block>
